data.description: This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with a study has so many upgrades! Open concept kitchen and living, both bathrooms have double vanities and granite countertops. 5 linen closets throughout! Plantation shutters on all west facing windows, 2” vinyl blinds on all other windows. Whole home guttering, walk in storm shelter, the whole 1 acre has been sodded to include a sprinkler system, wood look ceramic tile, black chain link fencing and so much more! Don't miss your opportunity to own this corner lot in the country.
